{"tid":192843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"晨早流流比人屌","createTime":"2017-04-08T23:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T00:38:37.000Z","uid":65174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a725931e1be9c6ac009d501e25ce7e054abe464e","tid":192843,"uid":65174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T23:28:23.000Z","msg":"我明白做生意好重視開門第一個客，但生意唔係屌返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說今朝諗住買啲野食，就係間鋪頭問有冇麵<br />\n佢答完有，有個呀叔埋黎買野飲又搞呢搞路，咁趕時間廢事等咁耐就話唔要<br />\n一話都係唔洗，個呀姐即時黑面，當住個呀叔面不停口咁屌我：朝早你唔要就唔好問，搞到我全日冇曬生意，唔要就唔好問呀嘛，朝早唔好問呀嘛⋯⋯<br />\n最後廢事比人屌足一日嘅關係就買左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知個麵硬撚到胃痛<br />\n<br />\n我而家祝你每日都得朝早第一單生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2422e4d28ad0d7b99e1b7e909b9e46d8e4c774a3","tid":192843,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T23:31:09.000Z","msg":"俾人屌你仲夾硬買?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8bbce3975f57670b8aaa8a96589e1fe44a53cb1","tid":192843,"uid":65174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T23:35:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾人屌你仲夾硬買?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見佢咁想賣就習慣性地心軟，而家諗返都好後悔對呢啲人有同情心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf11203df58e2ba5a8e77015a882825f60d11f3","tid":192843,"uid":8724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T23:38:14.000Z","msg":"零售業成撚日覺得頭單開唔順就會成日無數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2ca7b007b7127c88663af5ae7a9c06b81c6fc7","tid":192843,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T23:39:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>俾人屌你仲夾硬買?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見佢咁想賣就習慣性地心軟，而家諗返都好後悔對呢啲人有同情心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\